snippet.title: The Angry Birds Movie 2 - Under Pressure: Exclusive PlayStation VR Experience
snippet.description:
Straight from E3 The Angry Birds Movie 2: Under Pressure from XR Games takes players inside the world of the new movie as the birds and pigs must set aside their differences and work together as the crew of piggy sub on its way to save bird island and piggy island from a new threat.
